comments: Very helpful. Stays after class to help you if you need it. All tests, quizzes, and homework online. Voice somewhat monotone though. Somewhat has a different way of solving problems compared to the online homework.

This guy seems like he knows what he\'s doing as far as math goes, but he\'s not so good at teaching it in a way for people who aren\'t interested in math at all. Very monotone (I took him at 8am-- he didn\'t catch my attention). Nice guy though!
Only a TA in this class but extremely helpful! Gives multiple examples until he finds one that connects with you. Has a great sense of humor too.

This class was not hard at all and he seemed very willing to help anyone who asked. If you go to class and do the homework you will be able to get a good grade. He goes over everything that is on the homework, tests, and quizzes in class.
